{"type":"message","id":"37104d4a","parentId":"4f674ea6","timestamp":"2026-03-23T00:28:05.291Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I have a clearer picture:\n\n- 涨停池: 28只\n- 炸板池: 23只 (说明昨天炸板情况比较严重)\n- 跌停池: 13只\n\nSo the market has a lot of 炸板 (23 stocks broke the limit-up) and 13 stocks hit 跌停. This is clearly a \"退潮\" or even worse market phase.\n\nLooking at the 涨停详情:\n- 28只 total, many with multiple 炸板次数\n- 电力板块 has 7只 including several high-board stocks (韶能股份3板, 华电辽能5板, 华电能源2板, etc.)\n\n\n- 光伏设备板块 also showing strength with 5只\n\nThe 炸板率和跌停数量 paint a concerning picture: around 82% of limit-up stocks broke through, and with 13跌停 stocks, the market is clearly in a risk-off environment. I'm leaning toward classifying this as \"退潮\" given the high board positions like 华电辽能 at 5板 and 深华发Ａ also at 5板, though it could even be \"冰点\" given how widespread the selling pressure is.\n\nI need to recalculate the晋级概率 using the proper volume ratio formula.  量比 = 今量(今开5分钟量或全天预测量) / 过去20日均量, so I'm using last_close's volume divided by the 20-day average volume as my proxy. Since I'm working with end-of-day data, I'll use yesterday's volume for the calculation. For the晋级的判断, 退潮 phase has a 0.40 discount which is quite severe—let me test what happens if I use '启动' phase instead (0.85 discount) to see if it produces more reasonable probability estimates.\n\nLooking at the base晋级 probabilities from BASE_PROBS, even with '启动' phase the晋级概率 ends up quite low across the board. For a 1板 stock moving to 2板 with base probability 0.13 and an adjustment factor around 1.0, the calculation gives me roughly 11% with the 0.85 discount, which still feels underwhelming for what I'm trying to model.\n\nThe issue is that in a退潮 market, the phase discount of 0.40 is extremely punitive—it cuts even good stocks down to 3-8% 晋级概率. This explains why all the results are coming in below 15%. Given the actual market conditions—82% of limit-up stocks breaking, 13 limit-down stocks, and high-board stocks breaking while only 28 limit-up stocks exist—I'm looking at a clear退潮 or冰点 phase, which aligns with the pessimistic晋 rates I'm seeing. I'm going to stick with退潮 phase since it matches the market conditions and the screening purpose—I'll present the results as they are rather than trying to force a different phase. For the volume ratio calculation, I'm using yesterday's volume divided by the 20-day average volume, and I need to make sure I'm pulling the complete dataset rather than just the last 60 days.","thinkingSignature":"8483dfd02f200a4e6931b38862401dbaf4a6597abafeb602a84282b30e646d2b"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_46psvvmfdrvs_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd /home/gem/workspace/agent/workspace && python3 << 'EOF'\nimport sys\nsys.path.insert(0, '.')\nfrom astock.kline import get_kline\nfrom astock.predict import predict_stock\nfrom astock.auction import auction_ok\nimport akshare as ak\nimport baostock as bs\n\nbs.login()\n\n# Market sentiment\nzt_df = ak.stock_zt_pool_em(date='20260320')\nzt_count = len(zt_df)\nzb_df = ak.stock_zt_pool_zbgc_em(date='20260320')\ndt_df = ak.stock_zt_pool_dtgc_em(date='20260320')\nzb_count = len(zb_df)\ndt_count = len(dt_df)\nzha_ban_rate = zb_count / (zt_count + zb_count) * 100  # 炸板率\n\nprint(f\"市场情绪：涨停{zt_count}只，炸板{zb_count}只({zha_ban_rate:.0f}%)，跌停{dt_count}只\")\n\n# Sector analysis\nsector_zt = zt_df.groupby('所属行业').size().sort_values(ascending=False)\nprint(f\"\\n涨停板块：{dict(sector_zt)}\")\n\n# Phase determination\nif dt_count > 10 or zha_ban_rate > 50:\n    phase = '冰点'\n    phase_desc = '冰点（炸板率高，跌停扩散）'\nelif zha_ban_rate > 30:\n    phase = '退潮'\n    phase_desc = '退潮（炸板明显）'\nelse:\n    phase = '启动'\n    phase_desc = '启动'\n\nprint(f\"市场阶段判定：{phase_desc}\")\n\n# Full screening\nresults = []\nsector_count = dict(sector_zt)\n\nfor _, row in zt_df.iterrows():\n    code = str(row['代码']).zfill(6)\n    name = row['名称']\n    lb = int(row['连板数'])\n    sector = row['所属行业']\n    \n    kl = get_kline(code, days=120)\n    if kl is None:\n        continue\n    \n    # Correct VR calculation: yesterday volume / 20-day avg volume\n    vols = kl['vols']\n    if len(vols) >= 20:\n        vol_ma20 = sum(vols[-20:]) / 20\n        vr = vols[-1] / vol_ma20 if vol_ma20 > 0 else None\n    else:\n        vr = None\n    \n    kl_pred = {\n        'trend': kl.get('trend'),\n        'vr': vr,\n        'dif': kl.get('dif'),\n        'macd': kl.get('macd'),\n        'rsi': kl.get('rsi'),\n        'last_close': kl.get('last_close'),\n        'ma20': kl.get('ma20'),\n        'ma60': kl.get('ma60'),\n    }\n    \n    pred = predict_stock(code, lb, kl_pred, phase=phase)\n    sector_hot = sector_count.get(sector, 0) >= 3\n    ok_min, ok_max, vol_req, warning = auction_ok(code, name, lb, pred['jb_prob'], vr, sector_hot, phase=phase)\n    \n    # Filter: ok_min <= 7 and vr >= 0.5\n    if ok_min <= 7 and (vr is not None and vr >= 0.5):\n        results.append({\n            'code': code,\n            'name': name,\n            'lb': lb,\n            'sector': sector,\n            'jb_prob': pred['jb_prob'],\n            'ok_min': ok_min,\n            'ok_max': ok_max,\n            'vol_req': vol_req,\n            'warning': warning,\n            'vr': round(vr, 2) if vr else None,\n            'rsi': round(kl.get('rsi'), 1) if kl.get('rsi') else None,\n            'trend': kl.get('trend'),\n            'signal': pred.get('signal', ''),\n            'macd_state': kl.get('macd_state'),\n            'ma20_ma60': f\"MA20{'上' if kl.get('last_close', 0) > kl.get('ma20', 0) else '下'}方\" if kl.get('ma20') else 'N/A',\n        })\n\nbs.logout()\n\nprint(f\"\\n符合竞价条件股票: {len(results)}\")\nfor r in sorted(results, key=lambda x: -x['jb_prob']):\n    print(f\"  {r['code']} {r['name']} {r['lb']}板 晋级{r['jb_prob']}% 竞价{r['ok_min']}-{r['ok_max']}% VR={r['vr']} {r['sector']} | {r['signal']}\")\n\n# Distribution\ngt30 = [r for r in results if r['jb_prob'] > 30]\ngt15 = [r for r in results if 15 < r['jb_prob'] <= 30]\nlt15 = [r for r in results if r['jb_prob'] <= 15]\nprint(f\"\\n晋级概率分布：>{30}%：{len(gt30)}只, 15-30%：{len(gt15)}只, <15%：{len(lt15)}只\")\nEOF","yieldMs":110000,"timeout":120}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":16710,"output":1817,"cacheRead":27169,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":45696,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774225654124}}
