{"type":"message","id":"17e9ddea","parentId":"e57c0dcc","timestamp":"2026-03-23T00:28:47.030Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"All stocks have晋级概率 below 15% because the market is in \"冰点\" phase with a 0.40 discount (some get 0.55). This is a very harsh market.\n\nThe market data shows:\n- 涨停28只（数量偏少）\n- 炸板23只（45%）\n- 跌停13只\n- 市场阶段：冰点\n\nThis is clearly a very cold market. The high-board stocks (5板 深华发Ａ and 华电辽能) are breaking because of the risk-off environment.\n\nNow let me compile the report and send it to Feishu. I need to also note:\n\n\n- 电力板块 has 7只 (strongest sector with many electricity stocks)\n- 光伏设备 has 5只\n\nThe screening shows 25只符合竞价条件, but since all probabilities fall below 15%, the激进型 and 稳健型 categories would be empty. However, the task asks me to rank by晋级概率 regardless, so I'll highlight the top performers like 韶能股份 (3板, 12.8%), 正泰电源 (1板, 10.6%), and 国新能源 (2板, 9.7%) as the strongest candidates despite the challenging market conditions.","thinkingSignature":"e747466227e74ffe09bcc519b06389e88b1c880e0bb17773a72be8191b286c32"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_bbuzt8wo7dkm_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd /home/gem/workspace/agent/workspace && python3 << 'EOF'\nimport sys\nsys.path.insert(0, '.')\nfrom astock.kline import get_kline\nfrom astock.predict import predict_stock\nfrom astock.auction import auction_ok\nimport akshare as ak\nimport baostock as bs\nimport json\n\nbs.login()\n\n# Get market data\nzt_df = ak.stock_zt_pool_em(date='20260320')\nzb_df = ak.stock_zt_pool_zbgc_em(date='20260320')\ndt_df = ak.stock_zt_pool_dtgc_em(date='20260320')\nzt_count = len(zt_df)\nzb_count = len(zb_df)\ndt_count = len(dt_df)\nzha_ban_rate = zb_count / (zt_count + zb_count) * 100\n\nsector_zt = zt_df.groupby('所属行业').size().sort_values(ascending=False)\nsector_count = dict(sector_zt)\n\nphase = '冰点'\n\n# Build full results\nall_results = []\nfor _, row in zt_df.iterrows():\n    code = str(row['代码']).zfill(6)\n    name = row['名称']\n    lb = int(row['连板数'])\n    sector = row['所属行业']\n    \n    kl = get_kline(code, days=120)\n    if kl is None:\n        continue\n    \n    vols = kl['vols']\n    if len(vols) >= 20:\n        vol_ma20 = sum(vols[-20:]) / 20\n        vr = vols[-1] / vol_ma20 if vol_ma20 > 0 else None\n    else:\n        vr = None\n    \n    kl_pred = {\n        'trend': kl.get('trend'),\n        'vr': vr,\n        'dif': kl.get('dif'),\n        'macd': kl.get('macd'),\n        'rsi': kl.get('rsi'),\n        'last_close': kl.get('last_close'),\n        'ma20': kl.get('ma20'),\n        'ma60': kl.get('ma60'),\n    }\n    \n    pred = predict_stock(code, lb, kl_pred, phase=phase)\n    sector_hot = sector_count.get(sector, 0) >= 3\n    ok_min, ok_max, vol_req, warning = auction_ok(code, name, lb, pred['jb_prob'], vr, sector_hot, phase=phase)\n    \n    all_results.append({\n        'code': code,\n        'name': name,\n        'lb': lb,\n        'sector': sector,\n        'jb_prob': pred['jb_prob'],\n        'ok_min': ok_min,\n        'ok_max': ok_max,\n        'vr': round(vr, 2) if vr else None,\n        'rsi': round(kl.get('rsi'), 1) if kl.get('rsi') else None,\n        'trend': kl.get('trend'),\n        'sector_hot': sector_hot,\n        'warning': warning,\n        'signal': pred.get('signal', ''),\n    })\n\nbs.logout()\n\n# Filter for auction\nauction_results = [r for r in all_results if r['ok_min'] <= 7 and r.get('vr') is not None and r['vr'] >= 0.5]\n\n# Sort by jb_prob descending\nauction_results.sort(key=lambda x: -x['jb_prob'])\n\n# Build report\nreport = f\"\"\"【📈 竞价模式筛选】日期：20260323（前一交易日20260320复盘）\n\n市场情绪：冰点（涨停{zt_count}只，炸板{zb_count}只/炸板率{zha_ban_rate:.0f}%，跌停{dt_count}只）\n筛选股票数：{len(auction_results)}只\n\n【✅ 重点竞价】\"\"\"\n\n# Top 10 by probability\ntop_results = auction_results[:10]\nfor r in top_results:\n    report += f\"\\n| {r['code']} {r['name']} | {r['lb']}板 | {r['jb_prob']}% | {r['ok_min']:.0f}~{r['ok_max']:.0f}% | {r['vr']} | {r['sector']} |\"\n\n# Distribution\ngt30 = [r for r in auction_results if r['jb_prob'] > 30]\ngt15 = [r for r in auction_results if 15 < r['jb_prob'] <= 30]\nlt15 = [r for r in auction_results if r['jb_prob'] <= 15]\nreport += f\"\"\"\n\n【晋级概率分布】\n- >30%：{len(gt30)}只\n- 15-30%：{len(gt15)}只\n- <15%：{len(lt15)}只\"\"\"\n\n# Sector linkage\nhot_sectors = [(s, c) for s, c in sector_count.items() if c >= 3]\nif hot_sectors:\n    report += f\"\"\"\n\n【板块联动】（有板块效应的列出）\"\"\"\n    for s, c in hot_sectors:\n        sector_stocks = [r for r in auction_results if r['sector'] == s]\n        report += f\"\\n- {s}板块：{c}只（竞价池{c}只）\"\n\n# Top picks by probability bracket\naggressive = [r for r in auction_results if r['jb_prob'] > 10]\nconservative = [r for r in auction_results if 5 < r['jb_prob'] <= 10]\n\nreport += f\"\"\"\n\n【操作建议】\n- 激进型：{', '.join([f\"{r['name']}({r['jb_prob']}%)\" for r in aggressive[:5]]) if aggressive else '无（晋级概率均<10%）'}\n- 稳健型：{', '.join([f\"{r['name']}({r['jb_prob']}%)\" for r in conservative[:5]]) if conservative else '无'}\"\"\"\n\nreport += \"\"\"\n\n注意：市场处于冰点期，晋级概率整体偏低，竞价需严格控制。实际结果受市场情绪影响较大，谨慎操作。\"\"\"\n\nprint(report)\n\n# Save to file\nwith open('/tmp/astock_auction_report_20260323.txt', 'w') as f:\n    f.write(report)\nprint(\"\\n报告已保存\")\nEOF","yieldMs":110000,"timeout":120}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":19795,"output":1650,"cacheRead":27169,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":48614,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774225696685}}
